    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>289660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_300_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その魔物は、おまえたちが
背負う様々な負の要素が
具現化したもの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This monster is the embodiment
of the multitude of negative
sentiments lying in your heart.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
